high_descs: Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take the butterknife from the refrigerator.
Turn around and go near the potato.
Slice the potato into pieces using the knife.
Then turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the butterknife into the fridge.
Take the piece of potato from the sink.
Turn around and go near the potato.
Put the piece of potato into the sink.
Washed the potato in the sink.
Then take it from the sink.
Finally, placed the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the table washing from the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the fridge in the corner of the kitchen.
Take the butterknife from the bottom of the fridge.
Turn around and go to the potato on the kitchen counter in between the stove and sink.
Cut into the potato on the right.
Go back to the fridge.
Put the butterknife down on the higher shelf of the fridge.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Go to the sink next to the potatoes.
Rinse off the potato with water in the sink.
Look up to the sink.
Place the slice back on the sink, next to the rest of the sliced potato.
anns.task_desc: Cut a Potato slice, rinse it off with water, and place it on a Sink.

high_descs: Turn around to face the fridge.
Pick up the butterknife from the bottom shelf of the fridge.
Turn around to face the potato on the kitchen counter.
Slice the rightmost potato on the counter.
Head back to the fridge with the knife.
Put the butterknife in the fridge.
Turn around to walk to the potato on the kitchen sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter.
Walk to the larger sink on the left.
Rinse the potato in the sink.
Take out the sliced potato from the sink.
Place the sliced potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed slice of potato on the counter.
